Adnen Helali (Arabic) (a mụrụ na Sbeitla, 23 Machị 1975) bụ onye Tunisia na-ede uri na onye na-eme ihe nkiri, a mụrụ n'afọ 1975 na Sbeitli, Tunisia
Ọ bụ onye nkuzi asụsụ French na Sbeitla, na onye otu ihe nkiri Founoun nke dị n'obodo ya.
Adnen bụ onye guzobere na onye nduzi nke Sbeitla's Spring International Festival, kemgbe afọ 2000
na emume Rosemary nke Wassaia, obere obodo amoosu bụ nke Sbeitle.
N'afọ 2007, Adnen pụtara dịka Garrett Flaherty na Left for Dead; ihe nkiri egwu ọdịda anyanwụ nke America nke Victoria Maurette na-eme na nke Albert Pyun duziri.
